Name: HIVEMR-V1
Description: Internal patient_id from PIH's original Rwanda EMR

Name: IMB ID
Description: ID assigned by Inshuti Mu Buzima

Name: Incorrect IMB ID
Description: Invalid IMB IDs, having either an incorrect check digit or invalid format.

Name: OpenEMPI ID
Description: Specifies UUID of the identifier type that is used as the Global Identifier Domain (GID) in the MPI. It is generated by the MPI and is persisted in OpenMRS.

Name: Rwanda National ID
Description: National ID card with photo distributed to all Rwandan adults by the Rwandan Government from 2008
Format description: 16 numbers found on the ID card

Name: Social Security Number
Description: Number given out in the United States to track social security benefits and often used as a unique identifier..

Name: TRACnet ID
Description: Identifier assigned by Rwanda's national TRACnet system
